data.description: Look no further! This Ormond Beach home in the highly sought after Northbrook subdivison has it all!  Whether you want to cool off in the POOL  or warm up by the  fireplace, don't wait to call this home sweet home. Featuring a BRAND NEW ROOF completed in May 2021, new HVAC DUCTING throughout , 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms with upgraded vanities and granite, and luxury vinyl plank flooring. NO HOA, Fenced yard.  Conveniently located a few streets away from the river, and close to schools. Don't miss this one!
